    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle and heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Top, tail and slice your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> into discs</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>courgette discs </strong>to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5-6 min, turning halfway, until starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1693574212250-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1693574212250-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1693574212250-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1693574212250-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1693574212250-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>fresh</strong> <strong>tagliatelle</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the tagliatelle for 3-4 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> tagliatelle</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy</strong> <strong>pasta</strong> <strong>water</strong></p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1693574216403-x200.jpg",
