            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add <strong>half </strong>your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and <strong>half </strong>your <strong>cracked black pepper</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to the pan with the juice of <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s] </strong>and your <strong>vegetable stock</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up –<strong> </strong>this is your<strong> courgette & black pepper sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1693574227897-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1693574227897-x400.jpg",
