            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>courgette & black pepper sauce with fresh tagliatelle</strong> with a <strong>lemon</strong> <strong>wedge</strong> to the side</p><p>Tear over your<strong> basil</strong> and garnish with the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and<strong> remaining cracked black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
